          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Elimination of Double Subsidies for the Hardrock Mining Industry Act of 2015</b></p> <p> This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to disallow the percentage depletion allowance for hardrock mines located on land currently subject to the general mining laws, or on land patented under such laws.</p>]]></text>
